events.title: Machine Gun Kelly is arrested in Memphis

movie.title: Machine-Gun Kelly
movie.plot: George Kelly is angry at the world and scared to death of dying. A career bank robber, Kelly gets his confidence from his Thompson SMG and his girl Flo. After a botched robbery, Flo, Kelly and his gang try their hand at a more lucrative job: kidnapping.

events.title: Gerry Austin picks up John and offers to drive him south

movie.title: Goodbye Pork Pie
movie.plot: Gerry hires a car in Kaitaia with a stolen licence and travels to Invercargill with John, who's wife has just left him. The ultimate NZ roadtrip adventure.
